            "title": "Introduction"
        },
        {
            "endOffset": 108313,
            "parents": [],
            "secId": "se0010",
            "sentence": "We therefore propose a systematic investigation of proximity operators for perspective functions and show that the proximal framework can efficiently solve perspective-function based problems, unveiling in particular new applications in high-dimensional statistics.",
            "startOffset": 108048,
            "title": "Introduction"
        },
        {
