                {
                    "id": "se0090",
                    "title": "Applications in high-dimensional statistics"
                }
            ],
            "secId": "se0100",
            "sentence": "In the following, we will show that these estimators are based on perspective functions under the unifying statistical framework of concomitant estimation.",
            "startOffset": 131603,
            "title": "Penalized linear regression"
        },
        {
