            "secId": "se0010",
            "sentence": "The goal of this paper is to fill this gap by showing that they are amenable to solution by proximal methods, which offer a broad array of splitting algorithms to solve complex nonsmooth problems with attractive convergence guarantees [1,8,11,14].",
            "startOffset": 107620,
            "title": "Introduction"
